These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, card-games, woodworking, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, badminton, handball
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is soccer##2
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
3. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
4. the person who's sport is soccer is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | cooking  | gardening | woodworking | card-games  |
| Sport   | sailing | badminton   | handball  | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, apple, kiwi, kale
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, manager, doctor, musician
1. the musician is not to the left of the musician##8
2. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
3. the person eating nectarine is the manager##1
4. the person eating kale is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating apple##2
5. the person eating apple is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the security-guard##7
6. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
7. the security-guard is not to the left of the security-guard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | kiwi | apple          | kale | nectarine     |
| Job    | doctor      | musician | security-guard | manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, social-worker, security-guard, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, thriller, mystery, fantasy
1. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the security-guard##8
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the social-worker is in an even position##4
5. the chef is on the far left or far right##3
6. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
7. the chef is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | journalist | social-worker | security-guard     | chef |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | fantasy   | horror | mystery    |

