.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, funk, punk, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skiing, ice-hockey, cricket
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of country is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
5. the fan of jazz is the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | funk         | country   | jazz    |
| Sport         | skiing | cricket | ice-hockey | rowing |

