.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, time-travel, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skiing, baseball, parkour
1. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person watching thriller movies##7
2. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
3. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching satire movies##7
4. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's sport is skiing##7
6. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | time-travel | documentary | satire    |
| Sport         | basketball | parkour   | baseball   | skiing |

