3. the person eating plum is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person eating broccoli##5
6. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the fan of soul##8
7. the person eating avocado is the fan of soul##1

