.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, weightlifting, sailing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
2. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's sport is sailing##7
3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
5. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | coffee | soy-milk | lemonade   |
| Sport      | parkour | sailing | skiing  | weightlifting |

