3. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the fisherman##7
5. the teacher is not to the right of the lawyer##8
6. the lawyer is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the teacher##7

.:: Answer ::.
