.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, folk, rock, house
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, ship, car
1. the fan of electronic is between the fan of house and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
4. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the fan of rock is not the person driving the ship##6
7. the fan of house is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
8. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | house   | electronic | rock | folk |
| Transport     | car | motorbike       | bike  | ship    |

