.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapes, pumpkin, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, rock-climbing, chess, cooking
1. the person eating pumpkin is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | grapes        | watermelon | pumpkin      | artichoke    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | chess   | rock-climbing | cooking |

