.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, water, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, badminton, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person drinking 7up##7
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | 7up         | water    | lemonade       |
| Sport      | lacrosse | basketball | baseball | badminton |

