The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, animation, musical, sports
 1. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
 2. the person eating kiwi is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
 3. the person eating eggplant is the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the person watching animation movies##8
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating eggplant is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 9. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
10. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | carrot    | kale | eggplant | kiwi |
| Movie-Genre   | western | sports  | musical     | animation    |

