.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, carrot, broccoli, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, board-games, sudoku, hiking
1. the person eating broccoli is the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person eating broccoli is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person eating lemon##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
6. the person eating carrot is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person eating lemon##2
7. the person eating broccoli is in an even position##4

