.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, pony, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, taxi, motorbike, airplane
1. the owner of the goat is not the person driving the motorbike##6
2. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##7
4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
5. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
6. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
7. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | rat  | goat | turtle  | pony  |
| Transport   | van | taxi   | airplane | motorbike |

