.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, rat, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, train, roller
1. the person driving the scooter is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
4. the owner of the rat is the person driving the boat##1
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the boat##7
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person driving the train is between the person driving the roller and the owner of the rat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | goat    | bird | goldfish | rat |
| Transport   | scooter | roller      | train     | boat     |

 